Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不道歉不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,趁着还他这个时
